  <h1>REFUND &amp; CANCELLATION POLICY</h1>
  <p class="updated">Last updated: 10 July 2026</p>

  <div class="note-box">
    <strong>Note for site owner:</strong> This policy follows the standard Indian approach for digital goods — refundable only before delivery/download, or if there's a technical fault. Adjust the day-windows below if you want to be more generous.
  </div>

  <p>At FORGE, all products — e-books, workout plans, and online coaching — are digital and delivered instantly or near-instantly after payment. Because of the instant, non-returnable nature of digital goods, our refund policy is different from a physical-goods store. Please read carefully before purchasing.</p>

  <h2>1. E-Books & Workout Plans</h2>
  <p>Once an e-book or workout plan has been delivered to your email, the purchase is <strong>final and non-refundable</strong>. This is standard practice for digital downloads, since the content cannot be "returned" once accessed.</p>
  <p>Exceptions — we will offer a full refund or free replacement if:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>You received a corrupted, unreadable, or incomplete file</li>
    <li>You were charged more than once for the same order (duplicate payment)</li>
    <li>You did not receive any product within 24 hours of payment, and our support team could not resolve it</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Refund requests for the above must be raised within <strong>7 days</strong> of purchase.</p>

  <h2>2. Online Coaching</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Full refund if cancelled <strong>before</strong> your onboarding call / intake form is completed</li>
    <li><strong>50% refund</strong> if cancelled after onboarding but before your first week's program is delivered</li>
    <li><strong>No refund</strong> once your personalised program has been delivered and coaching has started</li>
  </ul>
  <p>If you're unhappy with your coaching experience, email us first — we'll try to resolve it (program adjustments, coach change, etc.) before any refund decision.</p>

  <h2>3. How to Request a Refund</h2>
  <p>Email <a href="mailto:forgebody@gmail.com">forgebody@gmail.com</a> with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your full name and registered email/phone</li>
    <li>Order/payment reference (from your confirmation email or Razorpay receipt)</li>
    <li>Reason for the refund request</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Refund Processing Time</h2>
  <p>Approved refunds are processed within <strong>5–7 business days</strong> and credited back to your original payment method (UPI, card, or net banking account used) via Razorpay. Depending on your bank, it may take a few additional days to reflect in your account.</p>

  <h2>5. Cancellations</h2>
  <p>You may cancel an order any time before completing payment — simply close the checkout page. Once payment is successful and the digital product is delivered, the order cannot be cancelled (see refund exceptions above).</p>

  <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>Questions about a specific order? Write to <a href="mailto:forgebody@gmail.com">forgebody@gmail.com</a> and we'll get back to you within 24–48 hours.</p>
